data.description: Stunning custom home on 1 acre lot with no HOA and resort style backyard! New Andersen Windows with LIFETIME warranty that will be transferred to buyers and solar will be fully paid off by seller! Open concept floor plan with tons of upgrades!! Gorgeous kitchen with new subway tile backsplash and custom brick accent wall and coffee bar! Over 3,700 sq ft, 4 bed, an office, 2 baths, and an entertainers backyard with pebble sheen saltwater pool with in ground filtration system. Walking up to the property you'll see 1 of 3 custom 8ft metal french doors, the 3 car garage with 220V installed for electric vehicle or welder and has dual paneled insulated garage doors and mini split ac. Located in the highly desirable Verrado school district! See list of upgrades!
